article_metadata.description: The first Democratic debate of the 2016 presidential race is Tuesday night, featuring front-runners Hillary Clinton and Bernie Sanders along with Martin O'Malley, James Webb and Lincoln Chafee. Watch the debate, and when you hear the words below, click to cover the squares. Make sure to yell “Bingo!” by sharing your card when you get five in a row.
